scoringPlays.text: C.J. Duncan 2 Yd pass from Kyle Shurmur (Tommy Openshaw Kick)
Jesse Ertz 15 Yd Run (Matthew McCrane Kick)
Kyle Shurmur 2 Yd Run (Tommy Openshaw Kick)

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur connects with Jared Pinkney for a 38 yard pass and moves the Commodores to the Kansas State three-yard line.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt WR Pinkney makes catch to put them in red zone

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur completes pass to C.J. Duncan for a two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt QB Shurmur hits Duncan to give them first score of game

videos.description: Kansas State QB Jesse Ertz runs for 27 yards and brings the Wildcats to the Vanderbilt 25-yard line.
videos.headline: Ertz's 27-yard dash moves Kansas State just outside red zone

videos.description: Jesse Ertz ties the game with 15-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Kansas State QB Ertz's rushing TD ties game

videos.description: Justin Silmon takes the handoff 23 yards and to the Vanderbilt 37-yard line.
videos.headline: Kansas State RB Silmon's 23 yard burst puts Wildcats into Vandy territory

videos.description: Kansas State QB Jesse Ertz is picked off by LaDarius Wiley and returned to the Kansas State 39-yard line.
videos.headline: Vandy CB Wiley's INT puts them inside K-State territory

videos.description: Ralph Webb is stripped and loses the ball, recovered by Kansas State defender Elijah Sullivan at the Wildcat's 13-yard line.
videos.headline: Vandy RB Webb's fumble ends drive for Commodores

videos.description: Kansas State QB Jesse Ertz is intercepted for second time of the night, this time by Ryan White.
videos.headline: Vandy CB Ryan White's INT puts Vandy just outside red zone

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur reach ball across the end zone line for the two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vandy QB Shurmur's gets hit, reaches across goal line for TD

videos.description: Behind Kyle Shurmur's go-ahead rushing touchdown, Vanderbilt goes on to defeat Kansas State 14-7 to improve to 3-0 on the season.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt tops Kansas State
